        "label": "IX-API API key and secret (client credentials)",
        "generateUrl": "https://sandbox.ix-api.net/auth/apikey/login?next=/",
        "setup": "Open the [sandbox](https://sandbox.ix-api.net) and create a new **API-Key** and **-Secret**. The Terraform provider docs show `api_key` and `api_secret`, and note `api_secret` can be supplied via the `IX_API_SECRET` environment variable. These credentials can be used as OAuth2 `client_id` and `client_secret` to log in to an IX-API implementation.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
